{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC16_RAN_100.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x14,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x13,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Ayesha, do you have a minute?<CR>I have big news."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "There was a village near Vierzeberg where all the villagers disappeared overnight..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x17,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "But recently, all those villagers came back!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x193,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "It seems so. I heard about that, too."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "So you knew about it?<CR>Well, it did create a buzz."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x4e,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "But the stories from those villagers are really interesting. I've been visiting that village frequently now."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x4f,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Villagers who disappeared and then all of a sudden reappeared..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x50,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "This is the perfect subject matter for a song to be passed down through tradition."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Ranun, could you be writing a song about that?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x195,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Exactly. I want to teach people about what happened in that village through song."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "That is my goal right now."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x18c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "When I disappear from this world, someone will play the melody that I have left behind..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x18e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "That's when all my effort will pay off."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Ranun, I didn't know you thought about things like that..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "In a world, a hundred of years from now...it'll be amazing if your music is still being played."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x4e,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "Right? Even if my name is forgotten,<CR>if my music still exists...then I'll<CR>be satisfied."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x4f,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "It'll be proof that we lived in this era."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x34,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Proof... To be able to leave proof behind...music is amazing!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x52,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "Hmhm, I'll make sure to create a song like that. I promise this to the shining stars in my eyes!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x35,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "You can do it! If there's anything I can help you with, I'll gladly do it!"
        }
    ]
}